## wizard 向导配置

```json
// wizard/install
[
  {
    "stepTitle": "基本配置",
    "items": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "field": "wizard_admin_username",
        "label": "管理员用户名",
        "initValue": "admin",
        "rules": [
          { "required": true, "message": "请输入用户名" },
          { "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z0-9_]+$", "message": "只能包含字母、数字和下划线" }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "password",
        "field": "wizard_admin_password",
        "label": "管理员密码",
        "rules": [{ "min": 8, "message": "密码不少于8位" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "select",
        "field": "wizard_db_type",
        "label": "数据库",
        "initValue": "sqlite",
        "options": [
          { "label": "SQLite（推荐）", "value": "sqlite" },
          { "label": "MySQL", "value": "mysql" }
        ]
      },
      { "type": "switch", "field": "wizard_enable_backup", "label": "启用自动备份", "initValue": "true" },
      { "type": "tips", "helpText": "请阅读 <a href='https://example.com/privacy' target='_blank'>隐私政策</a>" }
    ]
  }
]
```

**表单类型：** `text` / `password` / `radio` / `checkbox` / `select` / `switch` / `tips`

**验证规则：** `required` / `min` / `max` / `len` / `pattern`

