## 运行时环境声明

```
# manifest 中声明
install_dep_apps=python312        # python312/311/310/39/38
install_dep_apps=nodejs_v22       # nodejs_v22/v20/v18/v16/v14
install_dep_apps=java-21-openjdk  # java-21/17/11-openjdk
```

```bash
# cmd/main 中使用前设置 PATH
export PATH=/var/apps/python312/target/bin:$PATH
export PATH=/var/apps/nodejs_v22/target/bin:$PATH
export PATH=/var/apps/java-21-openjdk/target/bin:$PATH
```

